{"tid":2478271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文$1,400萬存款資產曝光　上任總統後身家大縮水","createTime":"2021-04-07T02:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T02:57:59.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"aafd01d0708546ba8c4f458a3b83f3a19c45a225","tid":2478271,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dTYbTOpc8AIr8r2YFrwG65wfGlM=/535x356/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U44ZM2KGBRHUHGMJJQTCHHNZI4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdTYbTOpc8AIr8r2YFrwG65wfGlM%3D%2F535x356%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU44ZM2KGBRHUHGMJJQTCHHNZI4.jpeg&h=136cf810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡英文上任總統後，財產大幅縮水。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n台灣監察院今（6日）公佈最新一期廉政專刊，根據總統蔡英文最新財產申報，存款共約5,284萬元新台幣（下同，約1,463萬港元）、股票413萬元（約114萬港元），存款較去年3月的申報資料多了400多萬元（約110萬港元），但與2006年擔任行政院副院長任內時有逾1億元（約2,770萬港元）存款相比，蔡英文上任總統後，財產大幅縮水。<br />\n<br />\n根據財產申報資料，蔡英文名下尚有位於文山區、內湖區2幅土地，以及2本自己的著作，另有事業投資110萬元（30萬港元），是位於台北市中正區的東道有限公司，以及每月9萬元（2.5萬港元）的租金收入。財產申報也顯示，蔡英文另有4幅土地，分別為台北市松山區2幅、台北市大安區1幅、新北市永和區1幅及2個房產，位於台北市大安區、新北市永和區，交由台灣銀行信託。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210406/XWPEELBKNNBUFMCZCIP2B6XBHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210406%2FXWPEELBKNNBUFMCZCIP2B6XBHM%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=d641b789\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210406%2FXWPEELBKNNBUFMCZCIP2B6XBHM%2F&h=254b7de4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210406/XWPEELBKNNBUFMCZCIP2B6XBHM/</a>"},{"pid":"b36ae74f3cf63a62f5bf681a2ad0d4cd735ec728","tid":2478271,"uid":377617,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"身家仲少過香港既一個